'''Hardaway Site''', also known as '''31ST4''', is an [[archaeological site]] near [[Badin, North Carolina]].  It preserves remains of prehistory, and is also important in the history of archeological methodology.<ref name="nhlsum"/>

It was declared a [[National Historic Landmark]] in 1990.<ref name="nhlsum"/>

